-md-ceo-ashishkumar-chauhan-minimum-qualifying-criteria-fno-rising-retail-losses-bse-angel-one-share-19859456.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-27T14:20:29","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"505302","title":"BSE faces declining share in a shrinking derivatives market.\nEquity derivatives trading fell in Feb 2026, even before higher STT rates.","summary":"BSE faces declining share in a shrinking derivatives market.\nEquity derivatives trading fell in Feb 2026, even before higher STT rates.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/stocks/bse-is-losing-share-in-a-shrinking-market-for-derivatives-ws-l-19854457.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-20T12:11:18","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"505209","title":"BSE's February ADTO dropped 21%, while NSE saw a 7% decline MoM.\nThe data highlights a notable reduction in trading activity for both exchanges.","summary":"BSE's February ADTO dropped 21%, while NSE saw a 7% decline MoM.\nThe data highlights a notable reduction in trading activity for both exchanges.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-20T11:19:05","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"501808","title":"Prop traders' index options market share rose by 230bps to 49.5% in FY26, per NSE data.\nRBI's new margin rules and STT hikes may lower market volumes, impacting small brokers and BSE earnings by ~10%.","summary":"Prop traders' index options market share rose by 230bps to 49.5% in FY26, per NSE data.\nRBI's new margin rules and STT hikes may lower market volumes, impacting small brokers and BSE earnings by ~10%.","url":"https://www.livemint.com/market/stock-market-news/prop-traders-index-options-market-share-surges-rbi-rules-impact-11771318336100.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-17T17:15:01","source":"Livemint"},{"id":"496055","title":"BSE gets SEBI approval to launch derivative contracts on midcap index.","summary":"BSE gets SEBI approval to launch derivative contracts on midcap index.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-13T22:32:11","source":"Li